# PDF Metadata Files

This directory contains JSON metadata files for each PDF in the `/pdfs/` directory.

## File Structure

Each metadata file corresponds to a PDF file with the same base name:

```
pdfs/my-document.pdf       →  pdf-metadata/my-document.json
pdfs/user-guide-v2.pdf     →  pdf-metadata/user-guide-v2.json
```

## Metadata Template

```json
{
  "title": "Document Title",
  "description": "Brief description",
  "filename": "document-name.pdf",
  "path": "pdfs/document-name.pdf",
  "size_kb": 1000,
  "created_date": "2026-05-11",
  "tags": ["tag1", "tag2", "tag3"],
  "summary": "One or two sentence summary",
  "key_points": ["Point 1", "Point 2", "Point 3"],
  "author": "Author Name",
  "version": "1.0"
}
```

See [PDF_MANAGEMENT.md](../docs/PDF_MANAGEMENT.md) for complete documentation.
